                     <interp inst="t18230409-118-person1062" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live with Miss Cummings. On the 13th of February I paid the money in question to the prisoner with a sovereign, a shilling, and a sixpence and saw him write this receipt.</p>
               <p>(read.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18230409-118-person1063">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18230409-118-person1063" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
