                     <interp inst="t18230409-118-person1063" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner at his master's house, and told him it was for receiving his master's money, and applying it to his own use; he said he had received about twelve different sovereigns.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a paper, stating his contrition for the offence, and begging for mercy.</p>
